This single-file program simulates the multi-file pattern using forward declarations. What does it print?

```cpp
#include <iostream>

int double_it(int x);
int halve(int x);

int main()
{
    std::cout << double_it(5) << "\n";
    std::cout << halve(8) << "\n";
    return 0;
}

int double_it(int x) { return x * 2; }
int halve(int x)     { return x / 2; }
```

